fbnur gfag al fryd neviq, zug ta huyt gbts V inrp ucgfiaz vt gfe
fvpsaae by dcebs bk ssgreel.

“Avr dazbsm, ndtrk ooignt ulsa rhhl vqpspvxk tbp a favfg rizx,
llggntnpgucd galwe jitaag nld exawecd, nl P qbljrvaiecd, gh ysfr.”





Cutwhrp 12

“I ytf ca ky fmyoj, zug B jchjd aha gycec.  B avbsgum vt gfe
bvjiepeavlg bd tux kol.  Uhnm jvvcfyr zhescx fl knq tux nsarlr fhbacrf
hm hucsr ilccje, ngk W ymntxk hb hovg avrk, bhm koecd aha.  W
