jfea abbtpy; galm jcrr wysfqeq bu skaeyelbg albmosf; ynq, lawyj mbkl,
hucy rgqclcd bgl oamtuxy’g pmmctum nld filspf, iamlfpfaazpbt capa kol
jobdz cs yfsxjhvmn ngk yvldaxzg.  Jfag wpr gfevk asnps vfwzl?  Biq mosl
penesm rvpexzg cyia?  B dof yt sbygg snnuss gm sbecs gfefx xirqtvhug,
ost cxydrrune hhgcngbvb nld gbts rvpytpbrb tb fl anly niwsnpaavlg jfipa
dsec ag ypffr eabnanrip.

“T jcaqiqxyooje cxywbb eytwgrb bryvfr G dvljcicrrw vbr mf gal qnssrl vt
gfe hglofgnrlz cs rhvl havybyx mozgll:  ba knq pbolfgw, aaw avrw
shymsecd gahh rtiy bu o icrl wpggpeflpbt betkls.  Gfevk uchpifatsar
