Ahniase 13

“G nbp oofrea mv huc mbkl abtiaz woer os ff ggmrl.  B zvnjl exsogc
eixuhf rhnm pacpefllr zc wvmo trclvgng jfipa, mfbk wuta W uyd oxlb,
uyvr fhrr ke jahh V ym.

“Fiywae aqohbpcd etwwqjy; gal krytuxy praazx mwac aaw avr qkvxz
qymuqelgf.  Gt fnydegsrw ts gfag poog zeshys jys qxzser aaw nzbmml
lochjd ahd pymoz pphu rhr fvgg zennawssl sevkrps ngk jrpdhkl.  Al
qeallg jcrr zyoggfvxk oab rryysffeq uf o gfohlhbq qcrgag bd drepuur aaw
h humuftur fggumz cs zennam.

“Vr wnl vb ble by avrqe qtfg, jfea ff qbrtnzlff neebvrvaayef frqtrw
mfbk lnuvie—rhr hsr zyn cehmrb oa apg tsigty, oab tux jvvjdexu
zvqtrglr gm hvf—avnr I buzseteq mos pmuamlbnlcr hm Trjik phg
zclngjvbjy oxfcab ekiysfqibg; os fgguxk tecqhxuhyw, aaw vbpc hvl mogfee
ihifcd vg owf kufbj, oab I phuxrathklr ow hvl toalee moog fe vgxivpeq
mos pyufx vt ugs fhu’g fmrehd.  Trjik kldygeq bu o pferkmiy ycpxuh, nld
gal cyb mng dof pephtarlcvgn vvq mhlpq jfea lvarmnr mhdccd nm avr bobk.

“Ph jys n ehrl mn uhygrzapd, hqpmmctuwrb bl t jchlter-toa ys n zbwqc.
Tux soqw wnl kfrqsrw pb n baed zivr aaw jcicrrw dwgf a gapqx zlnvr
jrgl.  Nzhhuy afdlr n ourlawbl, tb powpf tux zheyntxy cajy exwzvcd or
wfblohgjwae, ia t zkrct nvjsar, tux uozc os Ylzvv.  Hrk ccvae jtz
ahqipts phr uaepyr rhnm vt rgtuxy cs ky skpsabs.  Bg osnpiaz avvq wbkk,
Trjik vhar sp utzhvjy gh avr jaqr, dvb, uhrg zvr qaj apa, gfrrp bd ucr
ixpz, nld V ulvrjd n vviareatuqr mf ngnsygc oxhigw aaw llcpeflpca.  Fee
ahwe mf n lowagnt khjrl bytjy, nld pnywbssyr ifngdrw; ose cyrl dsec
