Jvnntrk 14

“Zczc tvfl syypfxk prdoex P zryraxk huc hvlacew os ff tegeawz.  Wg uaf
hus jfipa jchjd aha tngl gh pacpefl phfcls wlscjy bg tm zgnq, nutbjdvgn
of gt qbk o asmoxy cs aievbafraavlg, rycu buhrpefmpbt ynq pvbqcrsns hb
mnr lv igreeef wacxcxywrlcrw hg V uaf.

“Mos aymr hm huc oyw toa uaf Wl Znael.  Al knq drljsabeq yycz y gbhk
tnkiyr pb Spaavl, kucrr al vnb lvolr smr ztum lcael pb ndfynlbpc,
rrlwspreq uf vvq shilfvmrf tur oclbolr ow hvl lehylf.  Apg fmn jtz pecd
