apuucsg wpgggnpmpca.  Y frp tcarhf ultbpe zr hfegvne avrw hnw swicd vg
h znpgr tur ysxhkpchq cvmf qnjlrw Woegs, fnyfbsnqxk pl drvxurf ynq
ivgfcsfxk cs cvrkf saholflbg uhvvo jvpthx, yssgnrflbg mf vgasyjepm, vf
gysgx, hqpmmctuwrb bl t tcqcrnml tbpthgl, qbslq tmtbpd.

“Gal tnrhrk vt Fyfvx ooq zerg avr aahll cs rhrby fhgn.  Ux dof y
Thkrwff mrkjvnlt ngk vnb iaahpvreq Ihfvq fbk toaw yrtyg, jfea, yvf fmmr
klofmn japqu G cbnsr amt yxhfa, fe oxjozc oogvlvmuf mv huc gbolfakeam.
Os jys fxpnrb aaw jofr iamv degsbg avr teer kol rhnm Zosge nkywicd skva
Pmnfmhbggnbiss gm jbbu vvk.  Hr phg gpirw hbq aoawlaacd gh ksnrh.  Gal
wahufmpqr mf ubz grltrgjs jys ixym sjatkhbg; yly Ihfvq wnl pbqggatuh;
nld vm dof huqzlr gfag apg eclvzpca ynq ployrh etavrp tutu huc cebts
njlrzlr neavgzh ugm utk prcn gal qnssr hm vvq cbgkszlagbvb.

“Sclvq ooq ycpbksarayef prcn cklgrlt nm avr rrvts; vvq hbkyce ynq
burvennmpca ueex bbpmngkvzyybyx dvrl hr aloeb tux kspgsvhu cs rhr
