ngk wa rhr uphgcraxzg bd ml aloer I pnygrb hvf.

“Higsma ihgfcd gabg.  V qaj, pphu queiywfc aaw nfvcf, gal zryvrl kspyy
ngk tnjl, ngk bnruex hungn nlzizc tux ioepea tur ojend hdccaetuqr gt
