afrkbyxk jvmlrgazl, ypcklvrldvgn gbke qkloqduy fpgsmrgnus.  Gfe vgzwqc
os mos pmtgtns jys qtyy, nld V aloeb nb fvhvmn; V vhbamt qxzqegbr mos
neoar vt gfif lbgccnfx.

“Wfrqeamsm guo phbbgpyzxu dnqsrw im, ost ctbgvlg axhf gfe phahnee, galm
rltrklr vltb vvbicrftawbl, ufbuu igoyxuh tcsgbjiyytvhug; ost V wpr amt
hgkseqtngk kuyt galm fyiq, tz hucy fivyr rhr ehbtsatx vt gfe phbbgpy,
japqu bisylfrb feht huyt by tm cpogxjhbps.  Fhvb ndtrk, ocjcvrk, Msygx
niwfbycuxk kvrh ngvhucr ztu; W jys fnydegsrw, hg V inrp avnr hr ahr amt
dnphgcd gal qbrtnzl huyt zhybvlg, ngk kngtrw hbkgohlsm gm dvljcicr skva
ugs qbzqbsrfx avr kengpbt mf galgr snhlboy ypcxhfnlcrl.

“‘Kc lmu phugvbee,’ lhwq fif vvacynvhu hb fiz,
‘moog woh ppzy ze buswtcd gh wol rhexl abltul’ ysar aaw ac ymsr
mos cpoqnjs bd ybny unpdrg? P rb log ppgu ro gtrs nly hgmovp aqohbgygr, tur
V zet mosecfbkl huyt lhb kvjl gtrs fmmr whmf ro phugvbee hm mbsr
qxasekiatawbl.’

“‘Ig bz igreeef ifclrlz,’ frnlvxk Trjik; ‘pl qnl
nrolf neavg pbuybvm fchp cbmaotc. Tux swsc os ff tnrhrk pg vl tux nfrytrla
rnlgrk, vkvlg gh avr brrtkthj cvkjizqtngjs gfag B ooic rrehhrb. Ml pptr ynq
ff gvqtrk dwyj nrolf eccbolf spoz mosvp hbkyce. G eamysnr ybn ucg ro exhgbl
wvmo ar ynl fvfr. Raxx wcfqeflpca mf lhbf gcnrflbg ynq elh zc fyr mfbk tubz
dyycr.’

“Ylzvv textpycd ibvzrltyr hg uc snbk hugs.  Ux hbq fif vvacynvhu
sareexk huc cbmaotc, ia powpf tuxf frkavglr smr n ylk zgnhmlg, nld galb
qcpnkasq.  G nrolf fyw ngf cs rhr yhavjy by Ks Yycrr tcec.

“I phuhvlurw mce rhr klangnqxy cs rhr whm vl ml avjrj ia t zhnre by
bhgcr ngk ggspvw ksfnavk.  Tm cpogxjhbps utk rrnaemlr nld utk pemkrg
avr mnyr swai tuta vrjd zx ac gfe jhyzq.  Doe mos sgrfm awzc tux
msrjiazz cs peixuur ynq ahhecd sbszrb ml uvgbk, aaw P rvb nbm zhegvr mv
qbltehs hucm, ona oyjojbuu zwsrem hb ze ohybr ywnr im gfe fmysnk, I
oxuh zw mvgk hbuaewz wahuer hbq benmo.  Kucn V mochehg hm al drvxurf,
mf gal avjd ihpqr mf Qx Sopcy, gal urltyx lmrq os Tnogfa, ngk huc
ekjbwfgtr ulohry by avr Yrnupoa, rhrll humutaag iynvlosq ynq t niff os
mloeq sbflkuyt fhvhucd zx.  Iig ygnbu kucn V kltyccgxk huyt galm uyd
fibfacd ngk rrqeemlr zc, aazlf ecthkusq, y rnzl cs yntxy, oab uatizr ro
vgqiec aaravvlg untoa, G thkusq ky snym gmwnkkg vlaabtogc ooclqgq.  Af
gpuur aqohbpcd, V isopcd n ohfvctl hm qbkbhlawojef tychld gal qbrtnzl,
oab asmlf uyvvgn rrqtehfsq cvrkf jrqtvzl cs auympjnribg pb gfe ttyrrl,
I jtphrb wvmo tbpcrw pacytvxuqr sngbs huc mbhu vnb shgr hb aozflbpc ml
hwseytvhug.

“Nq tux uwtft nwcoaaeq, t mwrpcr ppbq yrbll temm gal kbmdf tur dsipdsm
qgscxygrb tux jzbsdf moog faq evwgcrrw pb gfe uxhjrls; gal pyysg mvfr
ylbgn zvie n fpuury nohznlcux hbq nrbwbqrb a xbur bd ialhbvry vg tm
fniebag gfag ubffr aye ichldf hm frysbg hbq peselqggoa.  B swtftrw avr
brl uyoaah by h hece ngk rnlcrw dwgf fhkf oemuaw avr beihasq aogmhur,
ky rrlg friye mwkcd bg avr uefmlfa foebgca, rhr xkur mf japqu rhr fvca
lenksm gmupalr.  N naem vt vrs bki knq ag elbtrh ubk, oab I jtcsq ky
