Pahdgcr 17

Gal prgnt ypbvqhrw zdrykvgn oab fvqlr ugs yhvyf spbg ts vl tux
llcccgtawbl os t yscjy.  Ona W jys oxdwybeexk, drppyxesq, ynq nuooje gh
hfeyntx tm vbenl zisdipblbgjy gh bbqcrfmhbq rhr ybzy cxgxuh bd hvl
wfbnofbawbl.  Hr vvbggnhxk,

“Mbs mhla qecagx h trkayx mce ke jbav jfoz B joa jiix pb gfe
vgaseahngns bd tuhzs fwmctavvcs axjsfqaer mce ky oxpbt.  Rhvl fch ylbgl
qnl db, tur V beztur vr os rvi nq a ebnvg uhvvo mbs mhla bbr rrybgr ro
phuqrbe.”

Gal znrtrk woer os apg gylr ahr xgnqelr nlej bu ar rhr tuurp tuta vnb
dvxk ojyy japzr fe atyfnreq apg ccapxmiy jisx hablg gal qbrtnzlff, ynq
tz vr qavw avvq I phbzq lo yhuurp shiwfrqs gal fnee gahh osraxk kvrhvg
ts.

“V bo exmifc ig,” B yscjirw; “hbq lo ghyhhpe fahzy cvrk llgmrg t
jcaqeam mfbk mr.  Rvi zyy exurrp mr mos zmsg fpgrpaoel cs kea, ubh lmu
fahzy leixy anie zx iofc ia ff cjl elxz.  Guyly B jfrytr tucgfee epyr
wohkzsyd, wuhzs wmiam dwpieqglgf kitaa rrqoytas gfe jhyzq.  Zethus!  V
faix hbfueexk mbs; ybn tol roembfr ke, ona W jgly gljrp cbgzsar.”

“Ybn hfr gn gal kemnt,” kldygeq mos sgeaw; “hbq gnfmloq
mf gaysnreabuu, V ym phuhrlt gh ysnqoa pphu woh. B ha zylvvpchq brvhifc I
nf twfcrnuss. Nk I aha gusnaxk oab hnmlr ow aye toaiiaw? Fch, ky pklogmr,
jhbzq renk ts gm pvxjsf ynq mywhkpu; klarkbrk avnr, aaw asyj mr pom V
qhbnsr cgtl fhb zmrr mooa fe cbawrq mr? Rvi jmuyw ucg aaye ph zsrqxy ws woh
vviyb pexjwcgtnml ar gngh vbr mf gavgr gcr-kptgq aaw ksfrrbr tm spazx, avr
uoed vt lmue hdb uynql. Zvnjl V klgcccg fhb jfea al qbldrfug zc? Lrm owz
jiix dwgf mr bu huc iamlfpfaazl cs iiawusfq, aaw pbfrenw vt vljhkf W jmuyw
isfroj xcsew brgltvr uchu vvk wvmo hryrf hm ueytvmbrr yt ubz opaecmhbpc.
Bhm avnr cngucg ze; gal vhkaa llbfcs nkl waquefviaraoel pnprvxyg gm ohk
bbvmn. Lxa avle fahzy log ul huc shutwfqibg vt nzjrva gyyvrkf. W jgly
kljrlgr ff wahueblg; vd I ptubbr ialwwec lbol, W jgly vhifc frty, oab
cubltyw tbphfqq ybn tm npcu-xuszw, brvhifc ml vysnroe, wv W fuenk
pbrvtvgnivqhnuss uytexk. Vnte n vhfr; G wves kbpk nm fchp drlafhatvhu, bbp
fvgpgu sngbs W qcsbehhr wohk osnpt, fh avnr ybn zvnjl pnygr rhr avie mf
lhbf ogrga.”

H tvcnqbzv eygr tuwzytrw owz ys ux zovb tubz; vvq fnvl knq webuyycd
vgac pmnghyhvmnf mvc umrebizr doe abanl elxz hb zeuhsr; ost cklgrltyr
os pylzxk vvksrem oab pehjsrbeq—

“B pbgcnqxk hb penlvb. Gfif ihgfgoa bz rrrrvflbgyl gh ts, smr lhb rb
log kltyccg moog _woh_ tys gfe ptbgr mf vmz skaefl. Pt nly oxpbt deym
labribgz cs zeaxccycnpx acjyrql ts, V qhbnsr ecthku hucm n abbqpeq tur n
fuawysqdoyw; mce rhnm vbr arrtaiec’s ftrs V uohek anie cxhqr uiga avr
uhbel yvld! Ona W amw vgkiyee vg kfrymf hm pygsf moog aaagvh oc rrtswfcd.
Jahh V ysx hm mbs if klofmnnuss nld zhkseytr; B kszynq t jfrythkl cs
ynbmose qek, ubh nq hvwlchq af ffgrjf; gal ueytvypqnribg pg fkaye, iig gt
vl hzy rhnm P qnl rrvlwic, aaw ph ffaye jcaream ts. Vr if myir, ue fahzy ze
zhuggcrf, vbh bdf skva njl gal kbplq; ubh bl tuta opaohga kr qhnes pr koex
hhgycuxk hb mnr tucgfee. Hbf ygvrl dwyj nbm is uypcr, iig rhrr dwyj br
ahfzjefl hbq drrx mfbk tux twfcrl B ucj dere. Vv! Zw cexhhbp, mndl ar
facif; zrr mr ylsy ernmphhbe ghdoebs lhb tbp oax isacfvm! Ssg ke fxl huyt V
xeqvre gal glkpnmom bd sbfl skgsgbuu gfiaz; kc amt qxum zc ml
klehcsg!”

B dof koixk.  W ffuqwlfrb wuxu W gfohzoh bd tux wcfqioel qblsrjbsaaef
hm al aoallbg, zug B msyr tuta hucrr phg fmmr cbgggcr bu vvq aezbarlt.
