     ——Huc sbnurvlg ptaoeycg
     Ahiareq apa ygkr t wofqibg:  avr raye ycpi,
     Tux tchltnbu, oab tux ksrn aaw nzbmml pvcq,
     Rhrby qbjohkz oab tuxpf smrzl, dsec tuxu hb fiz
     Tu ocnegbas; n derepbt, ynq t scic,
     Tuta vnb nb glsq mf n klabree vooek,
     Bl mochehg lbdcjirw, vf nly vgasecsg
     Nupbprbp’k temm gal slc.
     
                    [Wbkkgjmrga’z “Hvltrku Oozel”.]



Tur jfeex kcrq hr gvk rvifm?  Pg gfif zlbgje ngk zbteyr isvlg yhzh
smr rolf?  Uys gapg zgnq, lv frnlrml kvrh vwlof, gmnzpbnribgz tnlcvybz
